@startuml Submit Document Request Sequence
skinparam dpi 300
skinparam fontSize 14
skinparam entityFontSize 14
skinparam classFontSize 14
skinparam noteFontSize 14
skinparam actorFontSize 14
skinparam rectangleFontSize 14
skinparam participantFontSize 14
skinparam collectionsFontSize 14
!theme plain

actor Student
participant ":StudentDashboardView" as Dashboard
participant ":DocumentRequest" as Request
participant ":DocumentType" as DocType
participant ":LBCTracker" as LBC
actor Registrar

Student -> Dashboard: Select Document Type(s)
Student -> Dashboard: Select Delivery Method
alt LBC Delivery
    Student -> Dashboard: Enter Shipping Address
    Dashboard -> LBC: Create LBC Shipment
    LBC --> Dashboard: Tracking Number
end
Student -> Dashboard: Submit Request
Dashboard -> Request: Create DocumentRequest(s)
alt TOR Request (Graduate First Time)
    Request -> Request: Set price = 0 (FREE)
else TOR Request (Subsequent)
    Request -> Request: Set status = PENDING_TOR_COUNT
end
Request --> Student: Show Success Message
Registrar -> Dashboard: View New Request

@enduml